						               													<description>A small expansion for Mark Simonitch's Stalingrad '42 which adds an additional scenario covering the period from December 14th, 1942 through February 5th, 1943. &amp;#10;The scenario portrays the Soviet Little Saturn offensive following up on Operation Uranus, against the German allies of Romania and Italy. The German forces attempt at the same time to break the Soviet encirclement of the 6th Army with Operation Winter Storm. Counters are provided for the Soviet Ostrogozhsk-Rossosh Operation against the Italians and Hungarians, the Voronezh-Kastornoe Operation against 2nd Army, and the final offensive against Stalingrad, Operation Ring.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    1 8-page Little Saturn/Winter Storm Booklet&amp;#10;    1 half-countersheet&amp;#10;    1 Axis Setup card&amp;#10;    1 Soviet Setup card&amp;#10;    1 Turn Record track with Reinforcements&amp;#10;    1 updated Stalingrad &amp;lsquo;42 Rules Booklet&amp;#10;    2 updated Stalingrad &amp;lsquo;42 Player Aid Cards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
